parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering assist can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering assist warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel is hard to turn
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn while driving
the vehicle is difficult to maneuver
the steering wheel shakes abnormally
the power steering assist fault error message is displayed on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected shattering of the sunroof can cause driver distraction, loss of control, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Loud explosion sound
shattered sunroof glass around the edges
sudden and unexpected failure of the sunroof.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer case can cause loss of power, loss of control, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Internal failure of the transfer case
snapping off of the transmission
bent and leaking front U-joint of the rear drive shaft
transmission and transfer case fluid blown back on the undercarriage of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The use of incorrect tire size can affect vehicle stability, handling, and braking, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Tires mounted on the rear of the vehicle are not the manufacturer's recommended tire size.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty transfer case can cause unusual noises, fluid leaks, and potentially lead to loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Odd noises
burnt fluid
transfer case failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The push start button can inadvertently shut off the engine while the vehicle is in motion, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Engine turns off while in drive
requires restart by putting the car in park and applying the brake
slight pressure on the push start button can cause the engine to shut off.
